---
description: Preferred tech stack and implementation style
alwaysApply: true
---

Preferred stack:
- React
- TypeScript
- Vite
- Tailwind CSS
- Leaflet / react-leaflet
- TanStack Query
- Zustand only for lightweight UI state

Preferred architecture:
- frontend-first
- read-only MVP
- service-layer normalization
- modular UI
- clear docs

Avoid:
- unnecessary backend complexity
- premature optimization
- over-abstracted class hierarchies
- hidden business logic inside UI components
